Pakistan PM house bugged hacker claims to have hacked the bugger now blackmail?
text:
This story has been going on for the last few days where a hacker claims that he has hacked whoever was bugging the Prime minister house and has leaked audios of the Prime Minister Shebaz Sharif and his cabinet doing illegal things. Also seems to have proof of US using its influence with the Pakistan army to remove the previous PM Imran Khan. My question is that was the hacker really hacked the bugger or some Pakistan intelligence agency  just using hacker as a mouth piece.
